TITLE: Creating a Link with Dub SDK in Next.js API Route
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create a short link using the Dub TypeScript SDK in a Next.js API route. It creates a basic link with just a URL and returns the link object or an error response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dubinc/docs/blob/main/sdks/quickstart/nextjs.mdx#2025-04-10_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
