TITLE: Retrieving Link Analytics
DESCRIPTION: Fetches analytics data for a specific link with interval and grouping parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dubinc/docs/blob/main/sdks/quickstart/php.mdx#2025-04-10_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Dub\Models\Operations;

try {
    $request = new Operations\RetrieveAnalyticsRequest();
    $request->linkId = 'clmnr6jcc0005l308q9v56uz1';
    $request->interval = Operations\Interval::SevenD;
    $request->groupBy = Operations\GroupBy::Timeseries;

    $response = $dub->analytics->retrieve($request);

    if ($response->oneOf !== null) {
        // Handle the response
        print_r($response->oneOf);
    }
} catch (Throwable $e) {
    // handle exception
}
```

